data.description: Back on market through no fault of seller! Charming bungalow with open floor plan and huge, level yard in popular Ashford Park! Beautiful, gleaming hardwood floors throughout the entire home. Updated kitchen boasts granite counters, breakfast bar, stone backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and view to the living room. Cozy living room with vaulted ceiling and plenty of natural light. Custom built in wine rack and bar in hall. Updated bathroom with floor to ceiling subway tile and seamless glass shower.  Three spacious bedrooms with hardwoods throughout. Expansive covered back deck with fireplace and TV! Professionally landscaped yard with fenced in backyard, firepit, garden area, and shed. Freshly painted exterior! Walk to shopping and restaurants!  Conveniently located close to I-85 and 285!
